csx370.impl

Class ExtHashMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • csx370.impl.ExtHashMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<K,V>

    public class ExtHashMap<K,V>
extends java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<K,V>
    This class provides hash maps that use the Extendable Hashing algorithm. Buckets are allocated and stored in a hash table and are referenced using directory dir.
    See Also:
